        <p>
          Plot each of the following polar ordered pairs.
        </p>
        <sidebyside widths="32% 32% 32%" margins="0%">

          <p>
            <me>A:\,\,\left(3,\frac{11\pi}{12}\right)</me>
          </p>

          <p>
            <me>B:\,\,\left(2,-\frac{3\pi}{4}\right)</me>
